-- eval-one: вҠў= bodies вҖ” deterministic evaluation.

  yield symbols вүЎ "вҠў (declare cell), вҲҙ (soft body), вҠў= (hard body), вҠЁ (oracle), вҠЁ? (recovery), В§ (quotation), В«В» (interpolation), вүЎ (binding), вҶ’ (output access), в–ё (refinement), вҠўвҲҳ (evolution), вҠўвҠў (spawner)"

  yield execution-model вүЎ "eval-one via Kahn's algorithm: find cells with all givens bound, evaluate one, check oracles, freeze yields. Monotonic вҖ” yields only get bound. Document IS the state."

  yield patterns вүЎ "proof-carrying computation (LLM finds, code verifies), self-crystallization (вҲҙ вҶ’ вҠў=), evolution loops (вҠўвҲҳ rewrites soft cells), spawners (вҠўвҠў grows frontier), cell-as-agent (inbox вҶ’ dispatch вҶ’ act)"

