  вҲҙ Analyze the domain and decompose into components...

-- LLM evaluation (simulated):

  yield components вүЎ [
    "receive-diff: Accept a code diff and the repository's test suite as inputs.",
    "parse-diff: Parse the diff into structured changed-lines with file paths, line numbers, and content.",
    "scan-vulnerabilities: Analyze each changed line for known vulnerability patterns (injection, XSS, auth bypass, secrets exposure, buffer overflow).",
    "classify-severity: Assign severity levels (critical, high, medium, low) to each finding based on CVSS-like criteria.",
    "suggest-fixes: For each vulnerability found, generate a concrete code fix that addresses the issue.",
    "apply-fixes: Apply the suggested fixes to the original code, producing a patched version.",
    "run-tests: Execute the repository's test suite against the patched code to verify fixes don't break anything.",
    "verify-fixes: Cross-check that each original vulnerability is no longer present in the patched code.",
    "generate-report: Compile findings, fixes, test results, and verification into a structured review report."
  ]

  yield dataflow вүЎ [
    "receive-diffвҶ’diff вҶ’ parse-diff",
    "receive-diffвҶ’test-suite вҶ’ run-tests",
    "parse-diffвҶ’changed-lines вҶ’ scan-vulnerabilities",
    "scan-vulnerabilitiesвҶ’findings вҶ’ classify-severity",
    "scan-vulnerabilitiesвҶ’findings вҶ’ suggest-fixes",
    "classify-severityвҶ’severities вҶ’ generate-report",
    "suggest-fixesвҶ’fixes вҶ’ apply-fixes",
    "apply-fixesвҶ’patched-code вҶ’ run-tests",
    "apply-fixesвҶ’patched-code вҶ’ verify-fixes",
    "scan-vulnerabilitiesвҶ’findings вҶ’ verify-fixes",
    "run-testsвҶ’test-results вҶ’ generate-report",
    "verify-fixesвҶ’verification вҶ’ generate-report",
    "suggest-fixesвҶ’fixes вҶ’ generate-report"
  ]

