--
-- Total frames: 12 (0-11)
-- вҠўвҲҳ iterations: 2 (converged when critiqueвҶ’problems = [])
-- Cells evaluated: domain, cell-spec, decompose, design-cells, trace-readiness (Г—2),
--   simulate-oracles (Г—2), critique (Г—2), redesign, emit-program
--
-- Key observations:
--
-- вҠў= Observation 1: meta-design reveals oracle quality issues
--   The critique/redesign loop found 5 problems in iteration 1 вҖ” all related
--   to oracle precision (ambiguous, vague, missing). Iteration 2 found zero.
--   This suggests Cell programs benefit from at least one design review pass
--   focused specifically on oracle checkability.
--
-- вҠў= Observation 2: В§ quotation enables programs-that-write-programs
--   The entire designed program lives inside В§program as a value. Cells can
--   inspect, analyze, and rewrite it. This is Cell's metacircular capability
--   in action: the meta-cell-designer IS a Cell program that produces Cell
--   programs. The output .cell file is itself executable by eval-one.
--
-- вҠў= Observation 3: вҠўвҲҳ loop works for design convergence
--   The evolution loop (design вҶ’ critique вҶ’ redesign) converged in 2 iterations.
--   The convergence condition (zero problems) is structurally checkable.
--   This pattern generalizes: any task with a critique/improve cycle can use вҠўвҲҳ.
--
-- вҠў= Observation 4: spawner pattern natural for parallel scanning
--   The designed program independently discovered the вҠўвҠў spawner pattern
--   for vulnerability scanning вҖ” spawn one scanner per category, collect results.
--   This confirms spawners are a natural fit for embarrassingly parallel subtasks.
--
-- вҠў= Observation 5: proof-carrying pattern emerges from domain requirements
--   The code review domain naturally produces proof-carrying computation:
--   LLM suggests fixes (NP-hard creative work), crystallized cells verify
--   (P-time mechanical checks). The domain didn't request this pattern вҖ”
--   it emerged from the structure of the problem.
